.TH man 8 "30 May 2018" "0.1" "shy man page"
.SH NAME
shy \- inspecting bash scripts 
.SH SYNOPSIS
shy [command][file]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Shy is a program that inspects bash files for issues like:
.br
-Deprecated syntax
.br
-Outdated syntax
.br
-Invalid syntax
.SH OPTIONS
Enter the command then the file.
.br
-i, --inspect       Inspect the script for issues.
.br
-v, --version       Display shy version and exit.
.br
-h, --help          Describe command-line options and exit.
.br
-c, --commentary    Print commentary and exit.
.SH SEE ALSO
info shy 
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHORS
